cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.RO 

This paper deals with the use of unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs) as communication platforms in wireless networks, which is a topic related to networked systems (cs.NI) and information theory (cs.IT). The paper also proposes an optimization algorithm for joint trajectory and resource allocation, which involves control systems (cs.SY) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. Finally, the paper discusses the effectiveness of the proposed designs through simulation results, which is related to robotics (cs.RO).
